---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-ink-800/60 bg-ink-950/60">
  <div class="container-prose grid gap-12 py-16 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]">
    <div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-ink-50">
        <span class="text-copper-400">◆</span>
        PawPoller
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-400">
        A story-first multi-platform publishing pipeline for furry fiction writers. Built by one author getting tired of reformatting the same novella six times.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-copper-300">Product</h4>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-ink-300">
        <li><a href="#features" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#platforms" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Platforms</a></li>
        <li><a href="#get" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Download</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/knaughtykat01-prog/PawPoller/releases" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Releases</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-copper-300">Docs</h4>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-ink-300">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/knaughtykat01-prog/PawPoller/blob/master/SETUP.md" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Setup guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/knaughtykat01-prog/PawPoller/blob/master/documentation_guide.md" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Technical reference</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/knaughtykat01-prog/PawPoller/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Changelog</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/knaughtykat01-prog/PawPoller/blob/master/ROADMAP_PUBLIC.md" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Roadmap</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-copper-300">Community</h4>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-ink-300">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/knaughtykat01-prog/PawPoller" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/knaughtykat01-prog/PawPoller/issues" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Issues</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/knaughtykat01-prog/PawPoller/discussions" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Discussions</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/knaughtykat01-prog/PawPoller/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md" class="transition hover:text-copper-300">Contribute</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-ink-800/60">
    <div class="container-prose flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-xs text-ink-500 md:flex-row">
      <div>© {year} PawPoller · MIT licensed</div>
      <div>Built by writers, for writers.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
